    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up with nothing but the green light of a 90s computer. All there is on the screen is an investing program and a quota. You must escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terminal is a hacking game where you are an AI and have to solve puzzles to escape. In the format of a company's file system, you crack passwords, take notes, find out the truth, but most importantly: escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Included is a level editor where you can play community made games and share your own. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Evolving Investing Simulation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Expansive computer system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solving puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cracking passwords</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lots of hacking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find secret codes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Many minigames (like minesweeper!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078010/extras/8ec10b7c8bcfa3bb0894440b118f5a2f.poster.avif?t=1761930036\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078010/extras/8ec10b7c8bcfa3bb0894440b118f5a2f.webm?t=1761930036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078010/extras/8ec10b7c8bcfa3bb0894440b118f5a2f.mp4?t=1761930036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create and share your own levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play community made levels</p></li></ul>",
